@NODE "Mail_9" " Re: datatype transparancy "
From: Allan Odgaard <Duff@DIKU.DK>
Date: 09-07-99 23:19:21
Subject: @{b}Re: datatype transparancy@{ub}

From: Allan Odgaard <Duff@DIKU.DK>

On 08-Sep-99, Rod Schnell wrote:

> Thanks. BTW, regarding ak- datatypes, I did some checking. Nothing is
> crippled or disabled [...]

Well, if there were no alternative to *his* datatypes then they probably would
have been.
Like with the PPC versions of his datatypes - these will only output every
second line of the picture, if you haven't registered.

But crippled or not, if you use shareware you should register. Even though I
think it's a little bit greedy of Andreas to demand money for something
which is AFAIK based on other peoples work.

Regards Allan
-- 
     URL: http://www.DIKU.dk/students/duff/
