@NODE "Mail_60" " operator [][] ??? "
From: Allan Odgaard <Duff@DIKU.DK>
Date: 09-21-99 23:11:55
Subject: @{b}operator [][] ???@{ub}

From: Allan Odgaard <Duff@DIKU.DK>

Hi there,

Is there anyway I can overload a 2D-indexing?

I.e. if I have a picture class and wants to read pixel (x,y) I do:

   pixel = MyPicture[x][y];

Here I'd like the picture class to rotate x and y, before fetching the actual
pixel data.

Regards Allan
